title: BRIEF-SI Financial - Authorized A Stock Repurchase Program To Repurchase Up To 612,122 Common Shares
text:
May 9, 2018 / 12:31 PM / Updated 8 minutes ago BRIEF-SI Financial - Authorized A Stock Repurchase Program To Repurchase Up To 612,122 Common Shares Reuters Staff 1 Min Read
May 9 (Reuters) - SI Financial Group Inc:
* SI FINANCIAL GROUP - AUTHORIZED A STOCK REPURCHASE PROGRAM TO REPURCHASE UP TO 612,122 COMMON SHARES, OR ABOUT 5% OF CO'S OUTSTANDING STOCK Source text: ( bit.ly/2I5rDGL ) Further company coverage: (Reuters.Briefs@thomsonreuters.com)
